  cardName: The Curve Ball
  image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 2b331bae09b880f449fb33b601fa6383, type: 3}
  fact: "The Earth spins\u2014so the wind curves! This is called the Coriolis Effect.
    Because the Earth is spinning, wind doesn\u2019t blow in a straight line. It
    curves to the right in the Northern hemisphere and to the left in the Southern
    hemisphere. "
